data.description: Welcome to Seaford! This well kept, charming 2 bedroom 1 bathroom is waiting for its new owners! With the convenience of local shops, close to public schools, but out of town and no HOA, this will make a great first time home for you, or if you're looking to downsize and want less to maintain, look no further! This home is ready to move in and add your own touch to it! The roof has been updated within the last 2 years, and the original hard wood ceiling high cabinets give this home its charm! Out back you will find a nice sized shed with an attached car port! Get your showings scheduled now! This home is being sold as is; in the condition as it sits. All contents pictured in the photos will be removed prior to settlement!
